  {project_name: "Construction of UP Cebu Guesthouse Building in UPD", project_code: "IUPC2015-009", description: "", expected_outcome: "", remarks: "Pre-Bid Conference conducted on 02 Mar 2015\r\nBid Opening conducted on 16 Mar 2015\r\n\r\nDuring their visit to UP Cebu,  AVP Nestor Raneses and SPMO Head Isagani Bagus suggested that the bidding for the construction of the UPC Guesthouse in Diliman be conducted in UP Diliman.  To this end, UP Cebu is bidding out the design phase of this project but so far there has  been no takers.           ", percent_accomplishment: "2.0", percent_accomplishment_by: nil, bidding_contractor: "Two bidders participated in the A&E Design for the project:  New Adeson Construction Incorporated and K&K Builders with bids of P180,000 and P175,000, respectively.  OCA has  called the office of K&K Builders to get their feedback on the checklist faxed by SPMO.\r\n\r\nPost-qualification of K&K Builders, with the lowest bid of P175,000, is on-going.\r\n\r\nNotice of qualification was sent to K&K Builders last Friday, August 14, 2015.", bidding_number: 1, bidding_award: nil, bidding_proceed: nil, financial_budget: "2600000.0", financial_contract_price: "2615725.0", financial_actual_cost: nil, financial_source: "", timeline_target_start: nil, timeline_target_end: nil, timeline_actual_start: nil, timeline_actual_end: nil, university_id: 2, status: 6, completed_by: nil, bidding_remarks: "K&K Builders has been post qualified.", financial_remarks: "", timeline_remarks: "", has_components: false, has_phases: false, end_user: "", timeline_duration: nil, timeline_extension: nil, financial_variation: nil, classification: 1},
  {project_name: "Construction of Classrooms-Existing UP Cebu High School", project_code: "IUPC2015-010", description: "", expected_outcome: "", remarks: "Design by DPWH architect needed revision since it would cost more than P4.5M budget.    \r\n\r\nDesign by DPWH complete but will have to be re-estimated by the contractor.", percent_accomplishment: "1.0", percent_accomplishment_by: nil, bidding_contractor: "La Prueba Construction", bidding_number: nil, bidding_award: nil, bidding_proceed: nil, financial_budget: nil, financial_contract_price: nil, financial_actual_cost: nil, financial_source: "", timeline_target_start: nil, timeline_target_end: nil, timeline_actual_start: nil, timeline_actual_end: nil, university_id: 2, status: 3, completed_by: nil, bidding_remarks: "There have been several changes to the design of this project.  The final design is for two classrooms, one on the ground floor and one on the  second floor, as well as comfort rooms.   The building will be located at the side of the Undergraduate Studies Building, behind the to-be-built A.S. Extension Building.\r\n\r\nThe DPWH informed UP Cebu that construction would start soon but that the University should shoulder the cost and responsibility of cutting down    trees.", financial_remarks: "Government Agency - DPWH", timeline_remarks: "Contractor,  La Prueba Construction, will commence work in a few weeks - according to the DPWH.\r\n\r\nUP Cebu will request DENR for permit to cut down trees at the location of the building. \r\n\r\nDPWH inspected the site again today, August 27.  Contractor is waiting for tree-cutting permit from DENR before construction can start.", has_components: false, has_phases: false, end_user: "", timeline_duration: nil, timeline_extension: nil, financial_variation: nil, classification: 1},
  {project_name: "Renovation of Existing UP High School Buildings", project_code: "IUPC2015-011", description: "Renovation, rehabilitation and repair of existing UP Cebu High School building", expected_outcome: "Enhanced learning environment", remarks: "For final acceptance by End-user\r\n\r\nDPWH has issued a Certificate of Partial Turn-Over which  UP Cebu received on June 30, 2015.  As a pre-condition for signing the Partial Turn-Over,  Dean Liza Corro requested a Letter of Undertaking from District Engineer Nicomedes Leonor that all defects will be corrected before the final turn-over.  The turn-over was requested so that work which was not included in the Scope of Works of the contractor  -  such painting and tileworks -  could be undertaken by UP Cebu CDMO.   UP Cebu High School alumni have already pledged to donate in kind and cash to complete the project.", percent_accomplishment: "90.0", percent_accomplishment_by: nil, bidding_contractor: "La Prueba Construction", bidding_number: nil, bidding_award: nil, bidding_proceed: nil, financial_budget: "3000000.0", financial_contract_price: nil, financial_actual_cost: nil, financial_source: "", timeline_target_start: nil, timeline_target_end: nil, timeline_actual_start: nil, timeline_actual_end: nil, university_id: 2, status: 2, completed_by: nil, bidding_remarks: "Terrible workmanship.\r\n\r\nUP Cebu will do the rectification work to make the project functional.  Rehabilitated buildings have no paint or new tiles.\r\n\r\nRehabilitated buildings were inaugurated last Friday, August 14, 2015.   UPHS Batch 1985 has promised to shoulder the cost of installing new tiles while UPHS Batch 1995 has promised to shoulder the cost of painting.\r\n\r\nElectrical work needs to be done.  End-user is writing the donor to complain about various defects in the building.", financial_remarks: "Government Agency - DPWH", timeline_remarks: "La Prueba Construction received the Notice of Award (NOA) from DPWH on August 4, 2014.  Work has 