  {project_id: 357, component_name: "Design Services", description: "The Project includes the selection and management of the Consultant.  The required consultancy services are for Architectural and Engineering Design Services with the desired public assembly building, specifically convention center, architectural/engineering/green architecture expertise/experience.\r\n\r\nPhase 1 - Pre-design Services\r\nPhase 2 - Indicative Master Planning Services\r\nPhase 3 - Horizontal Engineering Design Services\r\nPhase 4 - Architect's Regular Design Services", expected_outcome: "", remarks: "*Financial proposal of the bidder with the highest rating in technical proposal opened on 26 May 2015.\r\n*Submitted pre-design services of Arce-Bailon-Arce approved by the Chancellor on July 09, 2015.\r\n*Submitted indicative master planning services (July 13) was approved by the Technical Working Group (TWG) on July 16,2015 and to be endorsed for the Chancellor's approval.\r\n*Phase 2 submission already approved by the Chancellor.\r\n*Arce-Bailon-Arce submitted horizontal engineering design services  (July 23) and presented their submission on July 29, 2015. Pending approval since there are comments and suggestions from the TWG.\r\n*Arce-Bailon-Arce submitted the revised horizontal engineering design however, there are still comments from the TWG as of August 05, 2015.\r\n*Arce-Bailon-Arce conducted topographic survey on the site on August 20, 2015.", percent_accomplishment: "35.0", percent_accomplishment_by: "2015-07-09 00:00:00", bidding_contractor: "Arce-Bailon-Arce Architects", bidding_number: 1, bidding_award: "2015-06-05 00:00:00", bidding_proceed: "2015-06-17 00:00:00", financial_budget: "8500000.0", financial_contract_price: "8489593.0", financial_actual_cost: nil, financial_source: "", timeline_target_start: "2015-06-26 00:00:00", timeline_target_end: "2015-08-31 00:00:00", timeline_actual_start: "2015-06-23 00:00:00", timeline_actual_end: nil, bidding_remarks: "", financial_r